  "title": "Junior Marketing & Operations Executive",
  "description": "<h3>Role Summary</h3><p>We are seeking a <strong>Junior Marketing & Operations Executive</strong> to support the growth of our training business.<br />This role focuses on <strong>corporate outreach, training coordination, and digital marketing execution</strong>, working closely with the Director and internal team.<br />This position is suitable for someone early in their career who is <strong>organised, analytical, and eager to learn</strong> about B2B sales, digital marketing, training operations, and SkillsFuture-funded courses.</p><h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><p><strong>A. Marketing Support & Corporate Outreach </strong><br />Support digital outreach to corporate clients<br />Follow up on enquiries via email, WhatsApp, and phone<br />Maintain and track follow-ups</p><p><strong>B. Marketing & Visibility Support</strong></p><p>Assist in EDM campaigns to corporate prospects and existing clients<br />Basic website content updates<br />Basic social media posting</p><p><strong>C. Operations & Coordination Support</strong></p><p>Support Director in coordinating registrations and training schedules<br />Provide accurate and timely communications</p><h3>What We Provide</h3><p>Exposure to SkillsFuture-funded training ecosystem<br />Structured processes and mentoring<br />Opportunity to learn B2B sales, corporate training, and digital marketing<br />Ample training will be provided</p><h3>Requirements</h3><p><strong>You want to work as part of a team to help grow our corporate client base.</strong><br />Diploma in Business, Marketing, Communications, or related fields, or with high interest<br />Able to communicate accurately and timely <br />Organised, specific with details, and able to work independently<br />Eager to learn, not shy to ask<br />Basic proficiency in Microsoft Excel, Outlook<br />Curious to learn and use Facebook, Instagram, LinkedIn, TikTok, AI tools to support our B2B outreach<br />Prior sales, admin, or customer service experience is an advantage</p>",
